data.description:
Nestled within the serene confines of Palm Bay, a picturesque coastal town, lies a charming four-bedroom, two-bathroom house that epitomizes modern comfort and tranquility. Built in the year 2019, this home boasts both the allure of contemporary design and the assurance of warranties that still embrace its appliances and structure.

Stepping inside, the spacious open floor plan instantly welcomes you. Sunlight cascades through large windows, illuminating the tastefully designed interior. The living area features a cozy yet sleek design meant to make any gathering or just relaxing moment memorable.
